Description:
    Creates (or updates) a Nitro frontend app

Options (for creation):
    name (optional): project name
    pre (optional): less or scss preprocessor
    js (optional): JavaScript or TypeScript compiler

Examples:
    yo nitro

        This will create or update a Nitro project

    yo nitro --name=myproject --pre=scss --js=JavaScript

        This will create a new Nitro project with scss support
